overview:
Everybody in the world needs a partner and is looking everywhere. dateIITians by introducing a new concept of Social Networking cum Social Dating made the thing easier. It is a growing online social dating and networking platform in the world and its growth is driven by its unique buddies concept and the range of services that it provides unmatched in the industry. It is based on the philosophy of a beautiful relationship which begins with buddy-ship (friendship) and results in developing and maintaining a meaningful relation, of course with the modern world definitions. dateIITians is all about meeting and socializing with new people, browsing through their profiles and checking for your compatibility level with them. Be it a loving relationship, a buddy-ship, a marriage or a networking relation, dateIITians hopes to empower, enrich & enable people to make their world more beautiful.

It is an endeavour to make it easier for the geeks out there in finding their perfect life partner. Moreover, everybody knows that good relationships begin with friendship only, so when you first become friends and then gradually start liking each other, then only the you can say that your relationship is developing and getting meaningful. dateIITians helps you do all those things that you do to get a date with someone through online social networking means (which is basically online social dating), while sharing your information with others. It helps you create profiles with your basic information; add buddies; grow your social network; flirt, express crush & propose people who you like and go on a date; while letting your other buddies see who you are flirting with, who you expressed your crush on and whom you are dating !

Our aim is to introduce a new world of Social Networking cum Social dating and to bring in new levels of buddy ship. It imitates the real life situation of social dating.
